234
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,120
Sawasdee krap, Khun Earth

235
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,000
Khun Tod

236
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:11,880
Khun Som-O

237
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,720
and Khun Arthit.

238
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:16,040
