245
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:35,920
Okay.

246
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:37,920
I leave him to you, Earth.

247
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:43,520
Sawasdee krap

248
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,960
Tod, have a seat

249
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:48,360
I call you here

250
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:51,800
